  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the binchotan grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, garlic, black pepper, salt, paprika, lime juice, and chili flakes.",
    "Add the broccoli florets to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Thread the marinated broccoli onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Brush the grill with oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the broccoli skewers for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally, until tender and slightly charred.",
    "Serve the skewers hot, garnished with additional lime juice and chili flakes if desired."
  ],
